<function>

access:  static public

name: staticValidIsInt

param: mixed, $value

return: bool

</function>

Used for testing Solar_Valid::callback() as a static method.

* Parameters:

 * mixed //$value//: The value to validate with is_int().

* Returns bool: True if $value is_int(), false if not.

